          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1636378228277-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1636378228277-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>wedges</strong> to one side of the baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then add the <strong>sausages</strong> to the other side of the tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for an initial 30 min or until the sausages are cooked through</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1636378233247-x200.jpg",
